title: 820-4924-A PPSUB_G3H shorted ground
message:
Hello everybody

I m working on liquid damaged 820-4924 board. Some one cleaned board, cant see burned items or corrosion. PPBUS_G3H is shorted ground when i inject voltage ppbus_g3h line after remove F7140 no where worming up:( checked every place board for any hot parts nothing. 

Note: Checked usb ,thunderbolt  and all connectors on board for damaged pins or like that.

What can i do next step?

title: 820-4924-A PPSUB_G3H shorted ground
message: Measure on diode mode from pin 2 from F7140 to all big coils, no one should give you a low value or beep.....

title: 820-4924-A PPSUB_G3H shorted ground
message: Yes there will be low resistance to the CPU Vcore coils. Measure F7140 to L7320, probably shorted and if so it will have taken out the CPU most likely.

title: 820-4924-A PPSUB_G3H shorted ground

title: 820-4924-A PPSUB_G3H shorted ground
message: Most likely a dead CPU.... What is the resistance from L7320 to ground???

title: 820-4924-A PPSUB_G3H shorted ground
message: Yeah if it was shorted the CPU will be dead, end of the line.
